  <hidden>true</hidden>
  <content>List all confluence macro documentation for a specified space.

= Parameters =

|=Parameter|=Description|=Required|=Default
|##reference##|The space reference to search the macros|No|The current doc space
|##columns##|The columns to show|No|doc.location,confluenceId,handling,importSupportQualifier,xwikiId

= Example Usage =

{{code}}
{{confluenceMacroDocumentationList/}}
{{/code}}

Or with the parameters:

{{code}}
{{confluenceMacroDocumentationList reference="MyConfluenceMacroDoc" columns="confluenceId,xwikiId"/}}
{{/code}}</content>
